### Create short link with custom slug
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/link/short
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "slug": "sof",
  "destination": "https://stackoverflow.com/"
}

### Create short link with random slug
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/link/short
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "destination": "https://www.linkedin.com/"
}

### Redirect
GET http://localhost:8080/sof
Content-Type: application/json
